   Updated     : 2026-03-26
   ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
   Purpose     : Global using directives for all Razor components in the
                 Framework subtree. Provides shared imports for layout
                 primitives, page templates, and reusable UI building blocks.
                 Mirrors essential BCL and Blazor namespaces from
                 Components/_Imports.razor while remaining independent of
                 Modules and page-level dependencies.
   ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
   Changes     :
     - 1.0.0  Initial implementation.
     - 1.1.0  Added PageTemplatesV2 namespace.
     - 1.2.0  Updated namespaces after folder renames.
     - 1.3.1  Removed invalid V2 namespace imports.
     - 1.4.0  Removed Components.Table import.
     - 1.5.0  Removed obsolete V1/V1.5 namespaces.
     - 1.5.1  Removed obsolete '@using AbsenceApp.Client.Framework.DesignSystem'
              which no longer exists in V2.
   ===========================================================================
*@

